  <brief_title>Non-selective Beta Blockers Versus EVL for Primary Prophylaxis of Esophageal Variceal Bleeding in Patients With Hepatocellular Carcinoma With Portal Vein Tumour Thrombosis.</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Randomized Controlled Trial Comparing Non-selective Beta Blockers Versus EVL for Primary Prophylaxis of Esophageal Variceal Bleeding in Patients With Hepatocellular Carcinoma With Portal Vein Tumour Thrombosis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
